title: Yannis Pappas
itunes:title: Yannis Pappas
description:
Yannis Pappas is back and it's more chaotic than ever.  He recounts saving Whitney's life in a dog fight, her peeing in the yard, and challenges her on everything she says.  Check out his podcast LONGDAYS with Yannis Pappas and his special BLOWING THE LIGHT on Amazon and Apple TV.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
